# JBang-fmt arguments
# To invoke:
# * check only (fails with exit code 1 if code not properly formatted):
#   `jbang jbang-fmt@jbangdev @jbang-fmt.args --check`
# * apply
#   `jbang jbang-fmt@jbangdev @jbang-fmt.args`
#
# Configuration:
# * apply custom eclipse style
# * Java 25
# * formats only server non-generated Java sources

--style config/eclipse-java-formatter.xml
--java 25
